":418884,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:09:20.000Z","msg":"咁樓主假期多唔係返工撚咁好似又真係冇咁大影響<br />\n至多係蝕book左酒店或者車飛<br />\n都叫做蝕得起<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返工撚係蝕每年僅有既AL <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚴重好多"},{"pid":"2524662698943f863bbbac2d042343ffad253909","tid":418884,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:10:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>坐香草樂桃都唔坐hkexpress啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD時間無咁靚 無咁平 <br />\n比uo更認真計行李 多少少即收 uo無咁嚴<br />\n但都好難講 純粹個人經驗 可能我好彩/唔好彩</blockquote><br />\n講漏左捷星，有咁多選擇都要揀口碑最差果閒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 計行李認真正常呀，坐廉航預左架啦</blockquote><br />\nPeach係每人計<br />\n即係你買20kg係只係當一個人<br />\n唔可以好似uo 20kg幾個人share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nUo 一樣有早機去晚機返<br />\n自己睇下高松 大阪 鹿兒島<br />\n唔要行李 去三日兩夜 五百有找，仲平過係香港"},{"pid":"4b3fe290c8c63eadbff0ad9e7eb73cdeb1be3fc3","tid":418884,"uid":28004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:22:33.000Z","msg":"搭uo唔係問題 唔好到時出事果陣喺度怨天怨地囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04029e960462b6e284ad97b8fb6ee358421414de","tid":418884,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:25:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>坐香草樂桃都唔坐hkexpress啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD時間無咁靚 無咁平 <br />\n比uo更認真計行李 多少少即收 uo無咁嚴<br />\n但都好難講 純粹個人經驗 可能我好彩/唔好彩</blockquote><br />\n講漏左捷星，有咁多選擇都要揀口碑最差果閒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 計行李認真正常呀，坐廉航預左架啦</bloc