g src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/233300_a53c8474fff7705e3efdad96f5466dea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F233300_a53c8474fff7705e3efdad96f5466dea.jpg&h=8e509af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飛唔同地方 稅會唔同 有機會更平</blockquote><br />\n一野bin落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我最平試過飛鹿兒島唔洗400蚊"},{"pid":"5bdd02a56d30081e9399a522c052151dcf836a94","tid":418884,"uid":22663,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T19:37:40.000Z","msg":"樓主好過果班坐因航就打曬飛機嘅傻鳩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3064c5c14defc39de640c5bad303052c4dda288","tid":418884,"uid":16949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T20:09:11.000Z","msg":"人人預算唔同<br />\n其實搶平機票冇問題<br />\n出咗黎做野嗰啲人如果要請AL旅行好心就畀貴少少買返正常airline<br />\n幫襯廉航好似今次咁出事蝕哂啲AL真係唔好喊"},{"pid":"1e856bd8bfe47bc7b5c59bf1ec43eb06d1f57f52","tid":418884,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T20:58:25.000Z","msg":"我唔係好明而家學生d價值觀<br />\n開口埋口話窮<br />\n但知自己窮居然唔係儲錢而係堅持要旅行洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係因為而家已經唔興儲錢定點？"},{"pid":"790bd7cf2c8a5c29fcbcedcf21f7d2b2fb4eb1ec","tid":418884,"uid":63782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T21:10:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔係好明而家學生d價值觀<br />\n開口埋口話窮<br />\n但知自己窮居然唔係儲錢而係堅持要旅行洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係因為而家已經唔興儲錢定點？</blockquote><br />\n不如你講下香港地儲錢有乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大把全職搵得多過學生都因為一世搵極都未必買樓 所以寧願去玩見識下 好過成世屈係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0011f6c7995799fad3c4e38e68cc4ac2c7557a3","tid":418884,"uid":29292,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"